00:23:27,720 --> 00:23:28,960
You.

587
00:23:30,080 --> 00:23:32,360
Can you blame me?

588
00:23:33,080 --> 00:23:33,760
Negotiations

589
00:23:33,760 --> 00:23:35,680
are about moves and countermoves.

590
00:23:35,680 --> 00:23:37,000
I didn't expect them to surrender

591
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:39,120
in the first round.

592
00:23:42,840 --> 00:23:44,280
No, ask him, Xiaoyu.

593
00:23:44,800 --> 00:23:46,080
Why don't you ask?

594
00:23:46,080 --> 00:23:49,120
Whoever asks first is in the passive position.

595
00:23:49,120 --> 00:23:49,960
You ask him.

596
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:51,120
But don't ask directly.

597
00:23:51,120 --> 00:23:53,360
Just pretend you don't care.

598
00:23:53,360 --> 00:23:55,000
Beat around the bush.

599
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:56,480
Give yourself a break.

600
00:23:56,480 --> 00:23:58,120
Drama queen.

601
00:23:58,360 --> 00:23:59,560
What do you know?

602
00:24:01,800 --> 00:24:02,680
Ask him now.

603
00:24:05,280 --> 00:24:07,160
Bao Xue should do this.

604
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:08,520
She is professional.

605
00:24:09,600 --> 00:24:11,600
Don't text. Call him.

606
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:20,840
Hello?

607
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:22,440
Hello, Xiaoyu.

608
00:24:22,800 --> 00:24:25,160
Could you ask Ms. You Shanshan

609
00:24:25,160 --> 00:24:26,640
why she didn't answer the phone?

610
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:28,760
Mr. Gu has called several times.

611
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:30,760
I'll tell her.

612
00:24:31,600 --> 00:24:33,680
I'm in a meeting. Gotta go.

613
00:24:35,120 --> 00:24:35,720
OK.

614
00:24:36,720 --> 00:24:37,040
What?

615
00:24:37,040 --> 00:24:37,680
What did he say?

616
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:40,080
Shanshan.

617
00:24:40,080 --> 00:24:41,800
Mr. Gu called you several times.

618
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:42,720
You didn't answer one.

619
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:44,480
No, he didn't.

620
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:46,520
Oh yes, he did.

621
00:24:47,520 --> 00:24:48,920
But look at this number.

622
00:24:48,920 --> 00:24:50,200
It is obviously chosen randomly.

623
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:51,600
I thought it was from

624
00:24:51,600 --> 00:24:52,840
an MLM organization.

625
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:54,520
Call him back now.

626
00:24:54,520 --> 00:24:55,720
He said yes.

627
00:24:56,640 --> 00:24:58,240
Great!

628
00:25:00,080 --> 00:25:02,200
See?

629
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:03,720
My way worked!

630
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:04,600
You both should learn.

631
00:25:04,600 --> 00:25:06,280
Especially you, Dai Xiaoyu. Shut up.

632
00:25:21,600 --> 00:25:22,600
Coming.

633
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:31,080
Mrs. Bai.

634
00:25:31,080 --> 00:25:32,840
Welcome.

635
00:25:32,840 --> 00:25:33,560
Come on in.

636
00:25:35,320 --> 00:25:36,600
Do I need to change to slippers?

637
00:25:36,600 --> 00:25:37,480
No need.

638
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:38,480
OK.

639
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,120
I got it.

640
00:25:41,600 --> 00:25:42,960
You can watch us play mahjong.

641
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:43,840
No problem.

642
00:25:44,200 --> 00:25:45,760
That's what I'm here for.

643
00:25:45,760 --> 00:25:47,040
You sit here,

644
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:48,520
and watch us play for a while.

645
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:50,320
After I win this game,

646
00:25:50,320 --> 00:25:51,640
I'll make you tea.

647
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:53,080
Sit here.

648
00:25:56,440 --> 00:25:57,560
How should we call you?

649
00:25:57,560 --> 00:25:58,440
I'm Lu.

650
00:25:58,440 --> 00:25:59,120
L-U, Lu.

651
00:26:00,520 --> 00:26:02,560
Where did you work before retiring?

652
00:26:02,560 --> 00:26:03,680
Peking University Seventh Hospital.

653
00:26:05,280 --> 00:26:06,480
A doctor!

654
00:26:06,480 --> 00:26:07,960
What specialty?

655
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:08,960
Pediatrics.

656
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:10,280
Are you doing background research?

657
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:12,320
It's ok.

658
00:26:16,720 --> 00:26:18,640
Your house is clean.

659
00:26:19,520 --> 00:26:20,480
You made the house a warm,

660
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:21,880
cozy place to live.

661
00:26:23,360 --> 00:26:25,240
I set a rule for myself.

662
00:26:26,240 --> 00:26:28,800
Things that will not be used in one year,

663
00:26:28,840 --> 00:26:31,280
and clothes that won't be worn in two years,

664
00:26:31,280 --> 00:26:32,760
will be disposed of.

665
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:35,440
I give them away if anyone wants them.

666
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:36,200
If not,

667
00:26:36,560 --> 00:26:37,600
I‘ll sell them

668
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:38,480
as waste recovery.

669
00:26:40,360 --> 00:26:42,040
Are your children in Beijing?

670
00:26:42,840 --> 00:26:44,880
They are all married.

671
00:26:44,880 --> 00:26:47,440
One is in the south of the city 
and the other in the north.

672
00:26:47,440 --> 00:26:49,920
They visit me on holidays.

673
00:26:50,320 --> 00:26:51,400
We make phone calls

674
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:52,640
if needed.

675
00:26:53,760 --> 00:26:55,720
You should hang out more often.

676
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:58,040
People our age

677
00:26:58,040 --> 00:26:59,520
can't stay at home all the time.

678
00:27:00,640 --> 00:27:02,480
You should be more socially active.

679
00:27:03,080 --> 00:27:03,840
Otherwise,

680
00:27:03,840 --> 00:27:04,840
you will grow old fast.

681
00:27:05,200 --> 00:27:07,040
You are so outspoken.

682
00:27:07,040 --> 00:27:08,720
Good attitude towards life.

683
00:27:15,040 --> 00:27:16,840
I'm here. Where are you?

684
00:27:16,840 --> 00:27:18,040
I'm on the terrace outside.

685
00:27:19,600 --> 00:27:21,040
Through the door, I'm on your right.

686
00:27:30,880 --> 00:27:31,480
Sit.

687
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:36,680
Thank you

688
00:27:37,280 --> 00:27:38,240
for coming to see me.

689
00:27:38,840 --> 00:27:40,080
Don't be a stranger.

690
00:27:40,520 --> 00:27:41,480
I'm here just to tell you

691
00:27:41,480 --> 00:27:43,240
that Xiaoyu now lives in Beijing.

692
00:27:43,240 --> 00:27:44,720
She invested in a restaurant.

693
00:27:45,120 --> 00:27:46,320
Invested in a restaurant?

694
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:48,840
Doesn't sound like her.

695
00:27:48,840 --> 00:27:50,560
It's true.

696
00:27:50,560 --> 00:27:52,160
That restaurant is called...

697
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:53,200
Crossbow...

698
00:27:53,200 --> 00:27:53,800
No.

699
00:27:53,800 --> 00:27:54,640
It's...

700
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:56,680
Crossroad Bistro.

701
00:27:57,920 --> 00:27:59,480
My ex, an interior designer,

702
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:01,000
is decorating the restaurant now.

703
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:02,640
He gave me Xiaoyu's phone number.

704
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:06,040
Give me her number, please.

705
00:28:06,040 --> 00:28:07,040
And,

706
00:28:07,040 --> 00:28:08,640
do you know where the restaurant is?

707
00:28:10,080 --> 00:28:11,080
I didn't ask about it.

708
00:28:12,840 --> 00:28:14,280
Could you please

709
00:28:14,280 --> 00:28:15,480
ask for me?

710
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:18,160
Don't tell them it's for me.

711
00:28:18,920 --> 00:28:19,920
Are you guys

712
00:28:20,520 --> 00:28:21,520
OK?

713
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:27,760
I didn't handle some things very well.

714
00:28:27,760 --> 00:28:29,040
Xiaoyu was mad at me,

715
00:28:29,040 --> 00:28:30,040
so she left.

716
00:28:33,240 --> 00:28:34,760
She hasn't changed her temper.

717
00:28:37,280 --> 00:28:39,440
You two have been together for a long time.

718
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,640
You should get married.

719
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:41,280
Yeah.

720
00:28:41,280 --> 00:28:42,480
I think so too.

721
00:28:43,800 --> 00:28:44,760
Plus,

722
00:28:44,760 --> 00:28:46,720
Xiaoyu's birthday is coming soon.

723
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:48,440
I want to go back and surprise her.

724
00:28:48,440 --> 00:28:52,400
And we can discuss the wedding.

725
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:54,120
OK.

726
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:55,880
I'll ask it for you.

727
00:28:55,880 --> 00:28:56,760
I will tell you when I know.

728
00:28:57,440 --> 00:28:58,240
Thank you so much.

729
00:28:59,280 --> 00:29:01,160
I'm talking about the overall effect.

730
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:02,920
But we have to calculate the cost.

731
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:04,600
Will the overall effect appear out of nowhere?

732
00:29:04,600 --> 00:29:05,000
No.

733
00:29:05,000 --> 00:29:06,680
It is piled up with our money.

734
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:08,080
They are all stated in this plan.

735
00:29:08,080 --> 00:29:09,360
I did not make additional requirements.

736
00:29:09,360 --> 00:29:09,720
So?

737
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:12,080
Then you can do it according to the plan.

738
00:29:12,080 --> 00:29:14,320
I don't understand why we are arguing.

739
00:29:14,320 --> 00:29:15,120
I mean,

740
00:29:15,120 --> 00:29:17,280
can you unite your opinions?

741
00:29:17,280 --> 00:29:19,000
I met three out of four shareholders.

742
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:20,760
Everyone has their own idea and changes it by day.

743
00:29:20,760 --> 00:29:22,160
Everyone wants to be the boss.

744
00:29:22,160 --> 00:29:23,480
What should I do?

745
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:25,600
Their thoughts are just fine-tunings.

746
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:26,440
A hundred fine-tunings

747
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:28,480
are equivalent to overturning the plan 
and doing it again.

748
00:29:29,440 --> 00:29:31,240
OK, I know what you mean.

749
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:33,160
Well then, just listen to me.

750
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:33,840
But your problem is,

751
00:29:33,880 --> 00:29:35,320
you often give up what shouldn’t be given up

752
00:29:35,320 --> 00:29:36,840
and insist on what shouldn’t be insisted on.

753
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:40,360
I don't know what to say.

754
00:29:40,360 --> 00:29:41,920
What do you say?

755
00:29:43,840 --> 00:29:44,520
Stop that.

756
00:29:44,520 --> 00:29:45,160
Excuse me.

757
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:45,680
Sorry.

758
00:29:46,120 --> 00:29:46,960
Stop.

759
00:29:48,320 --> 00:29:49,440
We should set some ground rules.

760
00:29:49,880 --> 00:29:50,560
First,

761
00:29:51,240 --> 00:29:52,600
you can provide constructive opinions

762
00:29:52,600 --> 00:29:54,320
after thinking thoroughly.

763
00:29:54,320 --> 00:29:54,800
Second,

764
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:55,560
decisions

765
00:29:55,560 --> 00:29:57,440
cannot be changed after twelve hours.

766
00:29:58,120 --> 00:29:58,880
Third,

767
00:29:58,880 --> 00:29:59,880
I have the final decision

768
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:01,120
on whether to adopt your opinions.

769
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:03,080
But if you...

770
00:30:03,080 --> 00:30:04,200
Think thoroughly.

771
00:30:06,040 --> 00:30:07,360
I have only one question.

772
00:30:07,360 --> 00:30:08,840
If I listen to you,

773
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:10,240
who will be responsible for overspending?

774
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:11,240
As long as you don’t make changes,

775
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:12,600
it won't be over budget under my watch.

776
00:30:12,620 --> 00:30:13,400
OK, you'll be the boss.

777
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:14,920
Any overspending will be 
deducted from your balance.

778
00:30:14,940 --> 00:30:16,000
Do you accept that?

779
00:30:17,160 --> 00:30:18,160
If you do, then fine by me.

780
00:30:19,760 --> 00:30:21,880
I have never seen someone like you.

781
00:30:24,360 --> 00:30:24,960
OK.

782
00:30:25,560 --> 00:30:26,640
People,

783
00:30:26,640 --> 00:30:27,840
let's keep working.

784
00:30:27,840 --> 00:30:28,880
We're in a hurry.

785
00:30:29,800 --> 00:30:30,920
Let's see the materials.

786
00:30:31,120 --> 00:30:31,920
No, I'm not going.

787
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:32,640
It's your call.

788
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:33,280
Wow, chinoiserie.

789
00:31:33,280 --> 00:31:34,560
Very attentive.

790
00:31:34,560 --> 00:31:36,280
He has all the light boxes ready for us.

791
00:31:35,120 --> 00:31:43,720
[Crossroad Bistro]

792
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:39,000
Beautiful.

793
00:31:41,040 --> 00:31:42,000
Let's go in and have a look.

794
00:31:54,680 --> 00:31:55,640
Welcome.

795
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:00,800
What?

796
00:32:00,800 --> 00:32:02,440
Anything wrong?

797
00:32:02,600 --> 00:32:05,280
I can't find a word to praise you.

798
00:32:05,560 --> 00:32:06,880
You startled me.

799
00:32:09,360 --> 00:32:10,160
What do you think?

800
00:32:12,320 --> 00:32:13,000
Flashy.

801
00:32:13,360 --> 00:32:14,480
It's raunchy...

802
00:32:14,480 --> 00:32:15,040
It's romantic.

803
00:32:15,040 --> 00:32:17,760
Storming an iron-wall pass.

804
00:32:17,760 --> 00:32:19,000
Starting the long march from now.

805
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:20,400
Are you posting chicken soup for the soul again?

806
00:32:20,920 --> 00:32:21,760
Wonderful.

807
00:32:22,520 --> 00:32:23,520
I divided the yard

808
00:32:23,520 --> 00:32:25,080
behind the front hall into two spaces.

809
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:27,960
One side is the indoor garden,

810
00:32:27,960 --> 00:32:29,440
and the other is private rooms.

811
00:32:30,640 --> 00:32:32,480
The lighting of the indoor garden

812
00:32:32,480 --> 00:32:34,920
makes customers feel like spring all year round.

813
00:32:35,480 --> 00:32:36,360
If you think

814
00:32:36,360 --> 00:32:37,760
it's a waste of space,

815
00:32:37,760 --> 00:32:39,840
you can move all these plants out.

816
00:32:40,120 --> 00:32:41,720
As long as you don’t find it ugly,

817
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:43,360
you can put them on the table.

818
00:32:45,520 --> 00:32:48,120
There are movable partitions in private rooms.

819
00:32:49,840 --> 00:32:51,800
Customers' needs for large space

820
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:53,760
or privacy can be met.

821
00:32:57,600 --> 00:32:59,600
This wall took me a long time.

822
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:02,240
You can’t afford to hang expensive paintings,

823
00:33:02,560 --> 00:33:04,280
but I think it’s too ugly to hang cheap ones.

824
00:33:04,880 --> 00:33:05,520
So I chose

825
00:33:05,520 --> 00:33:07,080
a lot of mirrors for decoration.

826
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:08,760
It doesn't cost much,

827
00:33:09,360 --> 00:33:10,800
and it's tasteful.

828
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:16,200
The fishes

829
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:17,440
are a gift from me.

830
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:19,080
I hope your restaurant

831
00:33:19,080 --> 00:33:20,040
runs as smoothly as a fish swims.

832
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:23,200
Isn't your name Yu Songyang?

833
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:25,360
You should give us some sheep.

834
00:33:25,360 --> 00:33:27,160
Why fishes?

835
00:33:28,040 --> 00:33:29,040
You picky women.

836
00:33:29,520 --> 00:33:31,400
My work is done here.

837
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:32,480
Perfect.

838
00:33:32,800 --> 00:33:34,880
I'll settle the balance for you in a while.

839
00:33:35,560 --> 00:33:36,640
You are the first client

840
00:33:36,640 --> 00:33:38,280
who's not late in paying the balance.

841
00:33:38,280 --> 00:33:38,960
Any friends of yours

842
00:33:38,960 --> 00:33:40,640
can enjoy 30% off in this restaurant for life.

843
00:33:40,960 --> 00:33:41,520
Thanks.

844
00:33:41,760 --> 00:33:43,240
Can the 30% discount be used as payment to you?

845
00:33:43,240 --> 00:33:43,800
Knock it off.

846
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:46,240
Sly.

847
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:49,560
Aren't there four shareholders?

848
00:33:50,040 --> 00:33:51,400
Who is the fourth one?

849
00:33:52,400 --> 00:33:53,800
The fourth shareholder is my cousin.

850
00:33:53,800 --> 00:33:55,080
She is filming out of town.

851
00:33:56,040 --> 00:33:56,800
A celebrity?

852
00:33:58,080 --> 00:33:59,560
That'll be good.

853
00:33:59,560 --> 00:34:00,320
She is an extra.

854
00:34:03,880 --> 00:34:06,600
Does You Shanshan pick on her as she does with you?

855
00:34:08,239 --> 00:34:09,239
Of course.

856
00:34:09,239 --> 00:34:11,159
But my cousin has a glib tongue,

857
00:34:11,159 --> 00:34:12,480
so Shanshan can't outspeak her.

858
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:14,639
But we are only joking.

859
00:34:14,639 --> 00:34:15,719
No one will get mad.

860
00:34:16,239 --> 00:34:18,760
You don't have problems with Shanshan, do you?

861
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:20,880
Why do you ask that?

862
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:22,679
I see you two arguing a lot.

863
00:34:22,960 --> 00:34:24,040
I don't want you to take it wrong.

864
00:34:25,080 --> 00:34:26,679
You Shanshan is

865
00:34:26,679 --> 00:34:28,320
quite straightforward,

866
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:29,760
and sometimes a bit mean.

867
00:34:30,719 --> 00:34:32,040
But she is awesome.

868
00:34:33,639 --> 00:34:34,719
Running a company,

869
00:34:34,719 --> 00:34:35,600
investing in stocks,

870
00:34:35,600 --> 00:34:36,719
and now opening a restaurant.

871
00:34:36,719 --> 00:34:39,120
I think she must be a very strong person.

872
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:42,280
No woman is strong on every side.

873
00:34:42,600 --> 00:34:44,560
She must have a soft side too.

